data.description: Income Producer! This two family home is conveniently located in the very desirable Pelham Bay section close to express bus to Manhattan, all major highways, shops & restaurants. First floor unit features 3 spacious bedrooms, living room, front sunroom, dining room & eat in kitchen. Second floor unit has 3 generous size bedrooms plus a nursery/office attached to master bedroom, plus a large completely finished walk-in & detached 2 car garage complete this property!
